data.description: Large Home with In-ground Pool! Lone Grove School District. Total Electric. Interior Features: XL Living Area w/ Stone Fireplace,Big Kitchen with Bay Window & Dining Area, Center Island, Walk-In Pantry, all rooms are cable/internet ready, Utility Room with Folding Table, Master has 3/4 bath and Huge Closet, Office/Bonus Room Located on upper Level, Attic Fan, Lots of Storage and Built-Ins. Attached 2 Car Garage. Exterior Features: Large Fenced Yard, Chlorine Pool w/ new liner & pump motor, storm cellar, Storage Building, Fruit Trees: 2 Apple, 2 Peach, 1 Pear, 1 Plum, 1 Apricot, 1 Fig. Price is FIRM.
